cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.MA, cs.SY 

The paper deals with channel modeling and capacity evaluation for millimeter wave (mmW) frequencies in wireless networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the transmission, processing, and utilization of information. The paper also involves network infrastructure and wireless communication, which suggests the categories cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper uses statistical models and simulations, which could fall under cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
